Ya kamata Amurka ta ninka yawan kudaden da take zuba jari a AI.
Yayin da kasar Sin ke kara samun karfin gwiwa a fannin kere kere, Amurka ta kamata ta ninka kudaden da take zuba wa a fannin kere kere, in ji Kai-Fu Lee, mai zuba jari da kuma dan kasuwa mai fasaha ta wucin gadi da ke aiki da Google, Microsoft da Apple.
An yi ta'aziyya bayan sassan gwamnatin Amurka sun yi sanarwa tare da AI duk da cewa Amurka gabaɗaya ba ta da wata hanyar amfani da AI.
A wannan shekarar da ta gabata, kasar Sin ta gabatar da wani shiri: don zama kasa ta farko a fannin kirkire-kirkire na AI nan da shekarar 2030.
"Ƙara yawan AI zai zama kyakkyawan farawa saboda akwai ƙasashe da yawa da ke bin Amurka da yawa. Kuma muna bin ci gaban AI", in ji Lee.
Sau biyu zuba jari zai taimaka wajen ninka damar samun babbar nasara a fannin kere-kere da ke faruwa a Amurka, Lee ya shaida wa CNBC a wata hira da ya yi a wannan makon.
Lee, marubucin littafin "AI Superpower: China, Sill Valley da New World Oder" wanda Houghton Mifflin Harcourt ya wallafa a wannan watan, shine shugaban kamfanin Sinovation Ventures wanda ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin kera kere-kere a kasar Sin, Face++.
A shekarar 1980 a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon ya yi aiki a kan tsarin aiki na fasaha wanda ya lashe mafi girman matsayi na dan wasan Amurka Othello kuma daga bisani ya zama mai gudanarwa a Microsoft Research da shugaban kamfanin Google na kasar Sin.
Lee ya yarda da gasar fasaha ta Amurka ta baya kamar ta Defense Advanced Research Project Agency ta Robotics Challenge kuma ya tambayi lokacin da na gaba zai taimaka wajen bayyana hangen nesa.
Lee ya ce: "Masu sukar a Amurka suna aiki tukuru don samun kudaden shiga daga gwamnatin tarayya.
"China ba ta shigo da masana daga cikin kasar ba, amma ta kasance mai zaman kanta", in ji Lee.
Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun ɗauki manyan mutane daga jami'o'i da yawa don yin aiki a kan AI a cikin 'yan shekarun nan.
Lee ya ce sauye-sauyen manufofin shige da fice na iya taimaka wa Amurka ta zama mai karfin AI.
"Ina ganin ya kamata a ba da katin kore a matakin AI ta atomatik", in ji shi.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kasar Sin ta tsara shirin bunkasa fasaha a watan Yulin 2017.
Hukumar kimiyya ta kasar Sin ta baiwa wadanda ke cikin cibiyoyin ilimi kudade kamar yadda National Science Foundation da sauran kungiyoyin gwamnati ba sa baiwa masu binciken Amurka kudi, amma ingancin aikin ya kasa na kasar Sin, in ji Lee.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kafa Cibiyar Hadin gwiwar Fasaha ta Artificial, wanda ke nufin masu ruwa da tsaki daga masana'antu da ilimi, kuma Fadar White House ta sanar da kafa kwamiti mai zaman kansa kan Fasaha ta Artificial.
