A lokacin da suke zama a West Virginia, wani tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara jawabinsa na yakin neman zabe a daren yau a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shine jawabin farko daga cikin jawabai biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da dakatar da jawabai a wurare da dama da suka hada da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da yake an riga an dakatar da kuri'un da aka yi a gabanin zabensa don cike gurbin kotun koli, Trump yana son gina goyon baya ga zaben tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa wanda 'yan Republican ke fuskantar barazanar rasa iko a majalisar dokoki lokacin da aka kada kuri'un a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi kifi a Kogin Virginia a daren yau, kuma ta yaya za ka iya kallon bidiyon?
An shirya birnin Wheeling, West Virginia don karfe 7 na yamma ET, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon jawabin Trump na duniya a kan layi a kasa ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Trump na iya magana ne game da wannan makon na neman shugaban kasa, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya fuskanci zargin cin zarafin jima'i, tare da amincewa da kuri'ar da majalisar dattijai ta yi na dakatar da shi har tsawon mako guda yayin da FBI ke gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan jawabi shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar zaben watan Nuwamba su sami wasu karin goyon baya.
A sakamakon haka, sanarwar da Shugaba Trump ya yi ta ce jawabai biyar da zai yi a mako mai zuwa za su mayar da hankali ne kan "masu neman aiki da masu ba da tallafi masu karfi saboda 'yan Republican suna kokarin karewa da kuma fadada yawan magoya bayansu a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai", a cewar wani wakilin Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga shugaban kasa ya yi tafiye-tafiye zuwa jihohi da dama kamar yadda zai yiwu saboda mun shiga wani yanayi na yakin neman zabe mai rikitarwa", in ji wani kakakin Trump, wanda ya ki bayyana sunansa.
An shirya shi ne don Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, wasan na daren nan na iya kawo magoya baya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma jan hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh", a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne dai Trump zai koma jihar West Virginia karo na biyu a cikin wata guda, jihar da ya samu kashi 40 cikin 100 na kuri'un da ya kada a 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na West Virginia, Patrick Morris, wanda ke cikin binciken.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrissey cewa shugaban ya zo ya yi kokarin tayar da shi", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
