HIV/AIDS: China ta samu karuwar sabbin masu cutar da kashi 14 cikin 100
China ta yi hasashen cewa yawan 'yan kasar da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Jami'an lafiya sun ce an yi wa mutane fiye da 820,000 allurar.
An samu rahoton sabbin mutane 40,000 a farkon rabin shekarar 2018 kadai.
Kusan dukkanin sababbin cututtuka an yada su ta hanyar jima'i, yana haifar da canje-canje daga tsofaffin.
Amma a lokacin, cutar HIV ta yadu cikin sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin sakamakon jinin da aka yi masa.
Amma adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HIV a wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin sun fada a wani taron da aka yi a birnin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da Aids a ƙasar Sin ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Yaduwar cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An haramta luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma ana ganin cewa akwai masu nuna wariyar launin fata.
Domin tsadar al'umma, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin dari na maza da ke yin jima'i da maza suna aure da mata.
Yawancin cututtuka na asali daga rigakafin jima'i ba su isa a cikin waɗannan dangantaka ba.
Tun daga 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar HIV a duniya a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa jami'an 'yan majalisa na GOP sun yi amfani da bayanan sirri, sun yi amfani da 'ƙarya mai haɗari' da 'ka'idar jinƙai'
A ranar Asabar, 'yan majalisa na Jamhuriyar Republican na Amurka Maxine Waters sun yi ikirarin cewa wani ma'aikacinta ya sanya bayanan sirri na wani dan majalisar dattijai na Republican a shafin Wikipedia na majalisa.
Democrat a Los Angeles ya tabbatar da cewa an tabbatar da wannan da'awar ne ta hanyar masana da kuma shafin yanar gizon "Matsayin Dama na musamman".
"Maƙaryaci, ƙarya da ƙarya mai banƙyama", Waters ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa a Twitter.
Rahotanni sun nuna cewa akwai adiresoshin gida da lambobin waya na 'yan majalisar dattijai na Amurka, Lindsay Graham na Carolina da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, biyu daga Utah.
Wani mutum da ba a san shi ba ya bayyana a shafin yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis a kan Capitol Hill a yayin da majalisar dattijai ke shari'ar zargin cin zarafin dan takarar kotun kolin kasar Brett Kavanaugh.
An yi ta'asa ne bayan wasu 'yan majalisar dattawa uku sun yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan yanar gizo na sirri kamar Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ba da rahoton cewa adireshin IP ɗin da aka ɓoye na gidan waya yana da alaƙa da ofishin Waters kuma ya ba da bayanan membobin ma'aikatan Waters, Hill ya ruwaito.
"Wannan tuhuma ba ta da gaskiya, duk ƙarya ce kuma ba gaskiya ba ce", Waters ya ci gaba.
"Ma'aikatana, wadanda ke da bayanan sirri, na sirri da tsaro sun lalace saboda zargin karya ne kuma babu gaskiya babu yadda za a dauki alhakin wannan bayanan.
"Wannan tuhuma ba ta da tushe, ƙarya ce gaba ɗaya".
Bayanin Waters ya haifar da saurin bincike a yanar gizo, gami da tsohon sakataren yada labarai na fadar White House Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan ƙin yarda yana da ban tsoro", in ji Fleischer.
"Wannan ya nuna cewa ba ta da sha'awar zama dan majalisa.
Wasu suna fushi sa'ad da aka zarge su da abin da ba su yi ba.
Ba sa bukatar su yi tawaye.
Ba su da ikon tambayar dalilin da ya sa suke zarginsa.
Suna bukatar su yi shiru kuma su zauna lafiya".
Fleischer ya bayyana cewa Waters ya yi kwatancensa da shari'ar da Alkalin Kotun Democrat Judge Kavanaugh ya yi, wanda masana kimiyya suka ce ya yi mummunan aiki a ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican da ke neman tsige Waters a zaben tsakiyar shekara, ya kuma yi tsokaci a shafinsa na Twitter.
"Babban idan gaskiya ne", in ji shi.
A cikin wata sanarwa, Waters ta ce ofishinta ya gargadi "iyakar hukumomi da hukumomin da ke bin doka game da wadannan maganganun karya.
"Za mu tabbata cewa an gano masu laifi", in ji ta, "saboda haka za a tuhume su bisa doka don ayyukansu na lalata da kuma cutar da kowane ma'aikacina".
