Mickelson, wanda ke wasa a shekara biyu na shekara ta 12 na wasanni na wasanni, ya zauna tare da Jim Furyk don yara hudu da hudu a ranar Asabar.
Maimakon zama a tsakiyar aikin, saboda yana son Amurka, ya lashe gasar cin kofin duniya sau biyar a matsayin shugaban kasar kuma ya ci gaba da wasansa a kan iyaka a cikin fatan magance matsalolin da ke damunsa.
