Wani mutum ya samu harbin bindiga sau da dama a Ilfracombe
Wani mutum ya samu harbi da bindiga sau da yawa yayin da yake dawowa gida daga wani biki da daddare.
An kashe wanda ya mutu a cikin shekaru 40 a Oxford Grove na Ilfracombe, Devon. An harbe shi a goshi, ciki da hannu.
Jami'an sun bayyana cewa harbin ya faru ne da misalin karfe 2:30 na safe a lokacin da ake sa ran za a yi zaben, kuma "harbin ya yi kama da na ɗan lokaci".
Wanda aka kashe bai ga fuskar da aka harba ba.
Raunukansa ba su da hatsari ga rayuwarsa kuma 'yan sanda sun yi kira ga shaidu.
Ƙarƙashin ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
A cewar jami'ai, akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon wata babbar girgizar kasa da tsunami a birnin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a kuma ana sa ran adadin zai karu.
Saboda rashin sadarwa, jami'an tsaro ba za su iya samun bayanai daga yankin Donggala da ke arewacin Palu ba, wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5.
Mutane sama da 16,000 ne suka tsere bayan bala'in a Palu.
Ga wasu bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ne, wanda ke a gabar teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, yana da mazauna kusan 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwa yayin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka afku.
Donggala wani yanki ne mai nisan kilomita 300 (180 mi) a arewacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Gundumar, wanda ita ce karamar hukumar lardin, tana da mazaunan kusan 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Yin kwalliya da noma sune manyan tattalin arzikin tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala.
Har ila yau, hakar ma'adinai na Nickel yana da mahimmanci a lardin amma mafi yawa za su kasance a Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da ambaliyar ruwa sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar hukumar rage bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, mutane sama da 200 suka mutu kuma an lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami na yammacin Donggala a shekarar 1996 ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin Pacific Ring of Fire kuma ana yawan fuskantar girgizar kasa.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar kasa da tsunami da suka faru a shekarar da ta gabata:
2004: A ranar 26 ga watan Oktoba wata babbar girgizar kasa ta afku a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh a Indonesia a arewacin tsibirin Sumatra. An yi ambaliyar ruwa a kasashe 14, mutane 226,000 suka mutu a gabar tekun Indiya kuma fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afku a yankin gabar yammacin Sumatra a karshen watan Maris da farkon watan Afrilu.
Mutane sama da 100 sun mutu a tsibirin Nias a gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: A kudancin tsibirin Java, tsibirin da ke da yawan jama'a a Indonesia, girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 6.8 ta haifar da tsunami a gabar kudu kuma ta kashe mutane sama da 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afku a kusa da Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta yamma.
Mutane sama da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 a tsibirin Mentawai ta haifar da ambaliyar ruwa mai tsawon mita 10 wanda ya lalata kauyuka da dama kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a Pidie Jaya a Aceh ya haddasa barna da tashin hankali a yayin da ake gargadin mutane game da bala'in girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004 da suka yi sanadiyar asarar rayuka.
Wannan lamarin bai haifar da wani rauni ba amma mutane sama da 100 ne suka mutu daga ginin.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afku a tsibirin Lombok amma mafi yawa a arewacin tsibirin inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon bude ido suka makale a tsibirin na ɗan lokaci.
An kama babban dan Sarah Palin bisa zargin cin zarafin iyalansa
Track Palin, dan dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska da mataimakin shugaban kasa Sarah Palin, an kama shi ne a kan zargin ta'addanci.
An kama Palin mai shekaru 29 a Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin cin zarafin dangi da kuma hana kama, a cewar rahoton da rundunar sojin Alaska ta bayar a ranar Asabar.
A cewar 'yan sanda, lokacin da wani masaniyar wata mata ya yi kokarin kiran 'yan sanda don bayar da rahoton zargin aikata laifi, sai ya kwace wayar daga hannun ta.
KTUU ta ruwaito cewa Palin tana tsare a Mat-Su Pretrial Facility kuma an tsare ta a cikin takardar kudi ta $500.
An ruwaito cewa a ranar Asabar Bulus ya bayyana a gaban kotu, lokacin da aka tambayi zarginsa, ya bayyana kansa ba shi da laifi.
Palin na fuskantar laifin aikata laifi na mataki daya zuwa uku wanda ke nufin zai iya fuskantar hukuncin daurin shekara daya a gidan yari da kuma tarar dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin aikata laifi na biyu, wanda hukuncinsa na kwana daya ne a gidan yari da kuma tara dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shine karo na farko da aka fara tuhumar Palin ba.
A watan Disambar 2017, an zarge shi da lalata mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don su ba da rahoton zargin cin zarafin.
Wannan shari'ar tana gaban kotun soji ta jihar Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016 an zarge shi da aikata laifukan tashin hankali na cikin gida da kuma mallakar makamai yayin da yake cikin maye wanda ya shafi lamarin.
Budurwarsa ta ce ya yi mata fyade.
Sarah Palin ta taba fuskantar suka daga kungiyar sojoji a shekarar 2016 bayan ta danganta halin tashin hankalin danta da PTSD da ya haifar da aikinsa a Iraki.
