Babban mai gabatar da kara na Amurka yana neman hukuncin kisa da ba a samu sau da yawa ba ga wanda ake zargi da kai hari a New York.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya na Amurka suna neman hukuncin kisa mai wuya a kan Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da kai hari a New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa ba a jihar don aikata laifi tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekaru 30, an zarge shi da amfani da motar Home Depot don kai hari kan hanyar keke a kan babbar hanyar yammacin Manhattan, wanda ya kashe masu tafiya da kekuna da yawa a watan Oktoba.
Don yanke hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov yana da niyyar kashe duk wadanda aka kashe takwas kuma yana da niyyar cutar da su, a cewar sanarwar kisa a kudancin New York.
Dukkanin zargin suna da hukuncin kisa, a cewar hukuncin kotun.
Makonni bayan harin, jami'an sashen lauya na tarayya na Amurka sun tuhumi Saipov da laifin aikata laifuka 22 da suka hada da laifuka takwas na kisan kai ta hanyar taimakon da aka yi da gangan, wanda yawanci ake amfani da shi a cikin laifukan da ake tuhumar da aikata laifuka da kuma amfani da tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Ana bukatar "shirye-shiryen da aka tsara da kuma tsari mai kyau", in ji mai gabatar da kara, ya bayyana halin Saipov a matsayin "mummunan hali, zalunci da kuma cin hanci da rashawa".
Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da rauni, haɗari da asarar dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco, da kuma abokansa, a cewar sanarwar da jihar ta bayar.
Wadanda aka kashe biyar daga cikinsu 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma kenan tun lokacin da New York ta Kudu ta yanke hukuncin kisa a shari'ar ta karshe.
An yanke wa fursuna Khalid Barnes hukuncin kisa a kan kisan wasu masana'antun magunguna biyu amma an yanke masa hukuncin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A shekarar 1953, an yanke hukuncin kisa a New York a kan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa saboda laifin yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe su biyu ta hanyar wutar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, dan asalin Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin sanin ya kamata a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya shaida wa mai binciken cewa yana jin dadin abin da ya aikata.
Saipov ya gaya wa jami'an da ke jagorantar kungiyar cewa ya yi kokarin kai harin bayan da ya kalli bidiyon kungiyar ISIS a wayar sa, a cewar karar.
'Yan sanda sun kara da cewa ya nemi a saka tutar ISIS a dakin sa a asibitin ma.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a kan tuhume-tuhume 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin Saipov ya ce sun nuna rashin jin dadin hukuncin da aka yanke.
Patton ya ce "muna ganin hukuncin kisa maimakon ɗaurin rai da rai ba tare da yiwuwar samun 'yanci ba zai kara tsawaita tasirin waɗannan abubuwan ga duk waɗanda ke da hannu".
Lauyoyin Saipov sun nemi a dakatar da hukuncin kisa.
