Ta yaya yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China zai kasance mai kyau ga gwamnatin China a Beijing?
Farawar yakin cinikayya tsakanin Sin da Amurka na nuna rashin kwanciyar hankali, kuma yayin da yakin ke kan hanya mai nisa; rikice-rikice tsakanin kasashen na iya zama da amfani ga China a cikin dogon lokaci; masana sun ce.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya fara yakin farko a farkon wannan shekarar ta hanyar kara harajin kayayyakin da China ke fitarwa ciki har da hasken rana da kuma aluminum.
Mafi mahimmanci, ta hanyar lissafin harajin shigo da kaya yana da tasiri har zuwa dala biliyan 200 (£ 150 biliyan) wanda ke shafar rabin kayayyakin da China ke shigo da su Amurka daga China.
Gwamnatin kasar Sin a Beijing ta yi ta amsawa a kai a kai bisa ga nau'i; a halin yanzu tana kara harajin 5 zuwa 10 bisa dari kan kayayyakin Amurka da suka kai dala biliyan 60.
China ta yi alkawarin fafatawa da Amurka ido da ido, kuma babbar tattalin arzikin duniya ta biyu na bukatar ta yi takaici a kowane lokaci nan ba da jimawa ba.
Don rage karfin tattalin arzikin Washington yana nufin neman bukatun; amma a fili, mika wuya ga Amurka na iya zama da wahala ga Shugaba Xi Jinping, shugaban kasar Sin.
Masana sun ce idan China ta shiga yakin cinikayya tsakanin kasashen biyu, zai iya amfanar kasar Sin a cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar rage yawan ci gaban tattalin arzikin biyu.
"Gaskiya ne cewa yanke shawara da sauri na siyasa, ko dai Amurka ko China, na iya haifar da yanayi wanda ba za a iya sarrafawa ba a cikin wata ƙasa; wanda a zahiri zai iya zama mafi haɗari fiye da yarda da juna kamar yadda yake a da", in ji Abigail Grace, mai binciken Asiya a Cibiyar Manufofin Tsaro ta Amurka.
Ministan harkokin wajen Syria ya ce:
Syria a shirye take ta karbi 'yan gudun hijirar da suka nemi komawa kuma suna bukatar taimako wajen farfado da kasar daga yakin da aka shafe shekaru bakwai ana yi.
Ministan harkokin wajen Syria Walid al-Moualem ya yi jawabi a gaban Majalisar Dinkin Duniya.
"Yanayin yankin a yau ya fi karko da tsaro saboda ci gaban da aka samu wajen yaki da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da gyara yankunan da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata don sake gina kasar.
Dukkanin abubuwan da ke faruwa a yanzu na iya sa 'yan gudun hijirar da ke neman komawa gida su bar kasarsu saboda ta'addanci da kuma tasirin tattalin arziki da ke shafar rayuwarsu da rayuwarsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa sama da 'yan Syria miliyan 5.5 sun tsere daga kasar tun lokacin da yakin ya barke a shekarar 2011.
Akwai mutane miliyan shida da ke zaune a kasashen da ke bukatar agajin jin kai.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta yi farin ciki da taimako don gyara kasar.
Amma ya ce ba zai yiwu a amince da tanadin tallafi ko tallafi daga kasashen da ke goyon bayan 'yan adawa ba.
Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder a Paris
Ƙungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder ta 2018 ta hanyar doke ƙungiyar Amurka a wasan ƙarshe da 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a filin wasa na National Stadium a waje da Paris; Netherlands.
Yanzu haka dai Amurka ta sha kaye a hannun kasashen Turai sau shida a jere kuma ba ta lashe gasar cin kofin Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta tashi sama lokacin da Danish Thomas Bjorn ya yi maki 14.5 da ya kamata ya doke Amurka.
Tauraron golf na Amurka Phil Mickelson ya yi gwagwarmaya a duk tsawon wasan, ya buga golf a raga na uku na rami na 16 wanda ya sa ya rasa ga mai wasan golf Francesco Molinari.
Gwanin golf na Italiya Francesco Molinari ya ci nasara a zagayensa; ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasa hudu da suka ci 5-0-0 wanda ba a taba samu ba tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a 1979 zuwa yau.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth ya buga 5&4 inda ya kasance a cikin jerin 'yan wasan da suka fi kasa a Turai da Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
Mai wasan golf na farko a duniya Dustin Johnson ya zo na biyu da na farko Ian Poulter na Ingila wanda zai zama dan wasan karshe.
Wanda ya shiga gasar Ryder Cup sau takwas shine Sergio Garcia na Spain wanda ya zama mafi kyawun Turai a duk lokacin da ya lashe gasar tare da maki 25.5.
