Shekarar da za a yi amfani da ita.
Don haka ina godiya ga Thomas da ya kawo ni cikin tawagar kuma ya amince da ni.
Ina matukar alfahari da samun lambar yabo.
"Wannan labarin na kungiya ne kuma ina matukar farin cikin taimakawa kungiyar", in ji Garcia bayan nasarar.
Ya ba da haske ga mabiyinsa John Ram wanda ya iya cin nasarar gasar golf ta Amurka Tiger Woods 2&1 ta hanyar wasa daya a ranar.
"Na ji girman kai mai ban mamaki, na iya doke Tiger Woods; Na girma ne saboda bin mutumin", in ji John Ram, mai shekaru 23.
Woods ya rasa dukkan wasanninsa hudu a Netherlands kuma yanzu haka ya kai 13-21-3 a gasar Ryder Cup.
Wannan adadi ne mai ban mamaki daga daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasan golf na tarihi; wanda ya lashe manyan wasanni 14 wanda ya kasance na biyu daga Jack Nicklaus.
Tawagar Amurka ta yi gwagwarmaya a duk tsawon karshen mako don cin nasara ba tare da wani banda ba har da Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau, wadanda suka kasance manyan 'yan wasa a duk wasan.
