Labarai kan Red Tide: Abin da ke faruwa a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Rahoton da aka bayar kwanan nan daga Hukumar Kula da Kifi da Daji ta nuna cewa raguwar Red Tide yana faruwa a wani yanki na Tampa Bay.
Rahoton FWC ya ce yanayin da ke faruwa a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier - yana nufin cewa yanayin ya ragu sosai.
Ruwan teku a cikin Red Tide ya shimfida a cikin wani yanki mai nisan mil 130 na bakin teku daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudu maso gabashin Lee.
Ana iya samun tabo a cikin nisan mil 10 daga gabar tekun al'ummar Hillsborough amma akwai wasu wurare a makon da ya gabata.
Bugu da ƙari, an lura da Red Tide a cikin al'ummar Pasco.
An ba da rahoton abubuwan da ke faruwa a cikin ko a gefen bakin teku na Pinellas a makon da ya gabata; ƙananan abubuwan da ke faruwa a gefen teku na Hillsborough; kuma akwai ƙaruwa a cikin Manatee da matsakaici zuwa babban abu a cikin Charlotte da manyan abubuwan da ke faruwa a cikin ko a gefen teku a cikin Lee da ƙananan abubuwa a cikin Collier.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahotanni a cikin Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da Collier al'ummomi.
A makon da ya gabata, ba a samu rahoton wani sabon abu ba a yankin arewa maso yammacin Florida.
